//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-island-2-haus-story-expansion-coming-in-november-2-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-island-2-haus-story-expansion-coming-in-november-2-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3513877" class="wp-caption-text"> 《死亡岛 2 豪斯》图片来源：Deep Silver</figcaption></figure><p>其中包括 K-ROSSBOW 作为一种精确的远程武器，可以爆炸目标，以及“屠宰和烧烤僵尸”的烤猪机。</p><p>将添加八张新的技能卡，允许从这些卡中产生实验性的和强大的套牌，而死亡群岛项目将“减轻你肩上的负担，同时将不死敌人粉碎成遗忘”。</p><p> <em>《死亡岛 2》</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/dead-island-2-review-3431863">在<em>NME</em>的评论中获得了五颗星中的三颗星</a>，表示当其他体验没有从同样的努力中受益时，令人印象深刻的现实恐怖感开始减弱。</p><p>里德·麦卡特说：“将文明的衰落置于最近废弃的豪宅、电影布景和通常由富人和名人居住的海滨之间，非常适合僵尸电影的社会讽刺——但不幸的是，该情节对这种原材料没有什么帮助。” 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3513878" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3513878" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-3513878 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-island-2-haus-story-expansion-coming-in-november-2.jpg" alt="《死亡岛 2 豪斯》图片来源：Deep Silver" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-island-2-haus-story-expansion-coming-in-november-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-island-2-haus-story-expansion-coming-in-november-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-island-2-haus-story-expansion-coming-in-november-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-island-2-haus-story-expansion-coming-in-november-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-island-2-haus-story-expansion-coming-in-november-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-island-2-haus-story-expansion-coming-in-november-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3513878" class="wp-caption-text"> 《死亡岛 2 豪斯》图片来源：Deep Silver</figcaption></figure><p> <em>《死亡岛 2 Haus》</em>将于 11 月 2 日推出<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation-4">PS4</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation-5">PS5</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>版本。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，Mintrocket 的潜水员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dave-the-diver-adds-new-missions-hireable-npcs-lobster-party-3513685"><em>戴夫 (Dave The Diver)</em>进行了大规模更新</a>，为玩家提供了新任务、新物种、可雇佣的非玩家角色和“龙虾派对”。</p><p> 《死亡岛 2》后的扩展包邀请玩家前往首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dead-island-2-expansion-invites-players-psycho-horror-malibu-dream-house-3513859">的“心理恐怖”马里布梦想屋</a>。</p> ;
基思·理查兹透露他每天都会向查理·瓦茨致敬https://www.nme.com/news/music/keith-richards-reveals-he-pays-tribute-to-charlie-watts-every-day-3513851?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=keith-richards-reveals-他每天都向查理·瓦茨致敬Liberty DunworthThu, 12 Oct 2023 10:53:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3513851 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="滚石乐队的罗尼·伍德、米克·贾格尔、查理·沃茨和基思·理查兹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位已故鼓手将在乐队即将发行的专辑中收录两首歌曲</p><p>基思<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/keith-richards-reveals-he-pays-tribute-to-charlie-watts-every-day-3513851">·理查兹 (Keith Richards) 的帖子透露他每天都会向查理·瓦茨 (Charlie Watts) 致敬，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="滚石乐队的罗尼·伍德、米克·贾格尔、查理·沃茨和基思·理查兹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keith-richards">基思·理查兹</a>透露，他每天都会向他的朋友兼长期乐队伙伴<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charlie-watts">查理·瓦茨</a>致敬。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-rolling-stones-every-album-ranked-in-order-of-greatness-3511878">滚石乐队：每张专辑按伟大程度排列</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>这位标志性的摇滚吉他手在接受<em>《霍华德·斯特恩秀》</em>采访时谈到了他与鼓手的密切关系，并分享了他每天对瓦茨的看法。</p><p> “我每天都想念查理，”这位 79 岁的音乐家透露，并补充说他每天早上都会为这位音乐家做一个特别的例行公事。 “当我走出卧室时，我首先看到的是……楼梯上查理的肖像——我总是在路上向他致敬。查理·沃茨是一个坚强的人。”</p><p>这位鼓手自 1963 年 1 月以来一直是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>阵容的一员<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/charlie-watts-rolling-stones-drummer-obituary-tribute-3027732">。他的去世于 2021 年 8 月宣布</a>，此前不久，他因手术导致并发症而被迫退出乐队巡演。他已经80岁了。</p><p>现在，这支由理查兹、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mick-jagger">米克·贾格尔</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronnie-wood">罗尼·伍德</a>组成的乐队在没有鼓手近六十年的情况下继续前进，并计划于下周五（10 月 20 日）发行他们的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-confirm-new-album-hackney-diamonds-and-single-angry-3494112">“Hackney Diamonds”</a> 。</p><p>这张专辑标志着他们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-confirm-new-album-hackney-diamonds-and-single-angry-3494112">第 24 张录音室唱片</a>，也是他们继 2005 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-the-rolling-stones-7763-312997">“A Bigger Bang”</a>之后 18 年来的第一张原创音乐合集。到目前为止，三人组已经分享了该项目的两首单曲： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-confirm-new-album-hackney-diamonds-and-single-angry-3494112">“Angry”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-share-lady-gaga-and-stevie-wonder-featuring-new-single-sweet-sounds-of-heaven-3506066">“Sweet Sounds Of Heaven”</a> （由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mick-jagger-working-with-lady-gaga-for-rolling-stones-sweet-sounds-of-heaven-3506722">Lady Gaga</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-wonder">Stevie Wonder</a>演唱）。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="基思·理查兹 (Keith Richards) 回忆滚石乐队鼓手查理·沃茨 (Charlie Watts)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/95Rra1VSFDs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-reveal-charlie-watts-appears-on-two-tracks-of-new-album-hackney-diamonds-3494170">瓦茨还被确认将参与其中的两首歌曲</a>《Mess It Up》和《Live by the Sword》，史蒂夫·乔丹为其余曲目提供鼓手。</p><p>在讨论瓦茨对他们的录音过程的影响时，理查兹说鼓手给他们的歌曲创作带来了一种“智慧”的感觉。 “他有感觉，他有智慧……摇滚乐不一定需要整套鼓，它与何时不敲击有关……如果你在创作音乐，沉默就是你的画布。”</p><p> “他会提出一些你没有真正想到的想法，”他补充道。 “[但是]同时，这是一个如此坚实的节奏。我从来不用担心任何事情，这让我们其他人可以自由地飞翔。”</p><p>其他为“哈克尼钻石”做出贡献的名人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mick-jagger-says-paul-mccartney-really-rocked-it-on-rolling-stones-collaboration-3502352">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰</a>和前滚石乐队贝斯手比尔·怀曼。您可以<a href="https://rollingstones.com/news/hackney-diamonds/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3513865" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3513865" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3513865" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones-2023@2000x1270.jpg" alt="罗尼·伍德、米克·贾格尔爵士和基思·理查兹于 2023 年 9 月 6 日在哈克尼帝国出席滚石乐队新专辑《哈克尼钻石》的发布会" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones-2023@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones-2023@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones-2023@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones-2023@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones-2023@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/The-Rolling-Stones-2023@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3513865" class="wp-caption-text">罗尼·伍德、米克·贾格尔爵士和基思·理查兹于 2023 年 9 月 6 日在哈克尼帝国出席滚石乐队新专辑《Hackney Diamonds》的发布会。图片来源：David M. Benett/Alan Chapman/Dave Benett/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在宣布这张唱片后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mick-jagger-reminisces-about-close-friend-charlie-watts-3502903">贾格尔还回忆起瓦茨，称他为“亲密的朋友”。</a></p><p> “我从 19 岁起就认识他了，我们经常出去玩，”他开始说道。 “查理和我除了在乐队中演奏之外还有很多兴趣。我们喜欢足球和板球……查理对[足球]非常了解。他小时候经常踢足球。他很不错。比我好多了。查理喜欢美丽的物体。他喜欢古董，喜欢家具。所以我们谈论了很多类似的事情。”</p><p>在滚石乐队的其他新闻中，贾格尔最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-are-already-working-on-their-next-album-3498047">证实乐队已经在准备下一张完整的作品</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-keith-richards-says-arthritis-has-changed-his-guitar-playing-3512240">理查兹透露他与关节炎的斗争影响了他的演奏风格。</a></p><p> “有趣的是，我毫不怀疑它有，但我没有任何疼痛，这是一种良性的版本，”吉他手说。 “我发现这很有趣，当我想，‘我不能再这样做了’时，吉他会告诉我还有另一种方法可以做到这一点。某个手指会移动一个空间，一扇全新的门就会打开。”</p><p>基思<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/keith-richards-reveals-he-pays-tribute-to-charlie-watts-every-day-3513851">·理查兹 (Keith Richards) 的帖子透露他每天都会向查理·瓦茨 (Charlie Watts) 致敬，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
